{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020/05/23/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"SetValue.NET","author":"Raúl Fernández de Córdoba","siteUrl":"https://www.setvalue.net","description":"Noticias, actualizaciones y mis experiencias sobre el mundo de las soluciones cloud","social":{"twitter":"rfcm83","facebook":"","linkedin":"rfcm83","github":"rfcm83","email":"rfcm83@gmail.com","rss":"https://feeds.feedburner.com/setvalue.net"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8e2664a2-9085-53cd-ae36-c558025f29bb","excerpt":"Hace poco se ha incluido una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones de Azure Active Directory. Azure siempre está incorporando alguna novedad, y ésta no podría…","html":"<p>Hace poco se ha incluido una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones de <strong>Azure Active Directory</strong>. Azure siempre está incorporando alguna novedad, y ésta no podría ser más útil.</p>\n<p>Tal y cómo se autodefine, su objetivo es ayudar a construir integraciones de alta calidad y seguras. Te muestra cuáles son las <em>best practices</em> y recomendaciones para ayudar a evitar descuidos habituales cuando nos integramos con la <strong>Microsoft Identity Platform</strong>.</p>\n<h2>App Registration</h2>\n<p>En la configuración del Azure Active Directory, en el apartado de <a href=\"https://portal.azure.com/#blade/Microsoft_AAD_IAM/ActiveDirectoryMenuBlade/RegisteredApps\" target=\"_blank\">App Registrations</a>, podemos seleccionar una aplicación que conozcamos cómo está configurada, y accedemos a su información del registro.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/29114/AppRegistration-Overview.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"App Registration\"\n        title=\"App Registration\"\n        src=\"/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/587b0/AppRegistration-Overview.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/8aea6/AppRegistration-Overview.png 243w,\n/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/44c61/AppRegistration-Overview.png 485w,\n/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/587b0/AppRegistration-Overview.png 970w,\n/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/5b795/AppRegistration-Overview.png 1455w,\n/static/7b850d78f6ccc98053540bd6b8e8446f/29114/AppRegistration-Overview.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Integration Assistant</h2>\n<p>En el menú lateral, encontramos un blade llamado <strong>Integration Assistant (preview)</strong>. Al acceder a él por primera vez, aparece un check list con el tipo de aplicación.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/29114/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant\"\n        src=\"/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/587b0/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/8aea6/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png 243w,\n/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/44c61/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png 485w,\n/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/587b0/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png 970w,\n/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/5b795/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png 1455w,\n/static/42d9dd05d0962b4eb56b61690e2447f1/29114/AppRegistration-IAssistant.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Una vez definido el tipo de aplicación que es, se evalúa y muestra el resumen de acciones verificadas.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Summary\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Summary\"\n        src=\"/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png 243w,\n/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png 485w,\n/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png 970w,\n/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png 1455w,\n/static/39d80a559f1c01bcc3d3facfba7b1da5/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>El resumen nos indica que no hay configurada una URL a la que redirigirse cuando se completa el login, lógico porque en concreto este registro está en blanco, no se ha configurado nada. Por otro lado, nos indica que si vamos a utilizar el flujo de autenticación implícito, debemos habilitar los ID Tokens. Y si queremos configurar un sign-out, debemos configurar también una URL de Logout.</p>\n<h3>Develop</h3>\n<p>En la pestaña de Desarrollo, está información básica,  y recomendaciones de implementación y de Experiencia de Usuario.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Develop\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Develop\"\n        src=\"/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png 243w,\n/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png 485w,\n/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png 970w,\n/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png 1455w,\n/static/275146748659d35d53a9326c6051fba6/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Estas recomendaciones nos dan acceso a artículos de la MSDN.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Develop Recommendations\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Develop Recommendations\"\n        src=\"/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png 243w,\n/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png 485w,\n/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png 970w,\n/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png 1455w,\n/static/85866837c19c5c04f4c82b6854eab3fe/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Test</h3>\n<p>En la pestaña de Test, se incluyen otras recomendaciones relacionadas con el Testing y con la Experiencia de Usuario. Algunas de estas últimas también recomendadas en el apartado de <strong>Develop</strong>.</p>\n<p>Sugerencias como que verifiques las políticas de Acceso Condicional por si pueden impedir a los usuarios utilizar la aplicación, resultan obvias, pero que no siempre reparamos en validarlo.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Test\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Test\"\n        src=\"/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png 243w,\n/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png 485w,\n/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png 970w,\n/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png 1455w,\n/static/e598448839fae9a003afe65ff01aeaf1/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Test.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Release</h3>\n<p>El apartado de Release, nos muestra cuatro apartados:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ownership</strong>. Nos recomienda agregar la información de contacto y que validemos si está realmente actualizada.</li>\n<li><strong>Branding</strong>. Incluir la información de marca con el logo y el nombre que mejor represente a tu compañía o producto, y por supuesto asegurarte de que no afecta a ninguna marca registrada.</li>\n<li><strong>Security</strong>. Minimizar y monitorizar manualmente la lista de propietarios de la aplicación o hacer rotados de credenciales.</li>\n<li><strong>End user experience</strong>. Incluir los certificados correspondientes si se está desarrollando una aplicación para Microsoft 365.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Release\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Release\"\n        src=\"/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png 243w,\n/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png 485w,\n/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png 970w,\n/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png 1455w,\n/static/648d0cadb05e99faa5da3e89e40438b4/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Release.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Monitor</h3>\n<p>El último apartado, encontramos recomendaciones de monitorización. Algunas ya incluidas en otros apartados, y otras orientadas al ciclo de vida de una aplicación.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Monitor\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Monitor\"\n        src=\"/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/8aea6/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png 243w,\n/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/44c61/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png 485w,\n/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/587b0/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png 970w,\n/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/5b795/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png 1455w,\n/static/d78b3c726262350d87d294f777248630/29114/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Integration Assistant Azure AD","date":"2020, May 23","description":"Azure Active Directory tiene una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones para facilitar la configuración de un registro de aplicación.","tags":["Azure","AzureAD","MicrosoftIdentityPlatform"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.94,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px","src":"/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/73822/Preview.jpg","srcSet":"/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/fe61d/Preview.jpg 485w,\n/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/9f4a9/Preview.jpg 970w,\n/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/73822/Preview.jpg 1940w"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/05/23/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/05/17/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GatsbyJS en GitHub Pages con Azure DevOps","tags":["DevOps","GitHubPages","GatsbyJS"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.941544885177453,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px","src":"/static/9a8dc88dfb9a0ae59190f9af6e6d1712/6b48d/DevOps-GitHub.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9a8dc88dfb9a0ae59190f9af6e6d1712/2f037/DevOps-GitHub.jpg 930w,\n/static/9a8dc88dfb9a0ae59190f9af6e6d1712/23f4e/DevOps-GitHub.jpg 1860w,\n/static/9a8dc88dfb9a0ae59190f9af6e6d1712/6b48d/DevOps-GitHub.jpg 1940w"}}}}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/05/30/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Durable Functions","tags":["Azure","Functions","Serverless"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.941544885177453,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px","src":"/static/f8e5e063265e9bce9de8ad1b54603359/6b48d/Functions.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f8e5e063265e9bce9de8ad1b54603359/2f037/Functions.jpg 930w,\n/static/f8e5e063265e9bce9de8ad1b54603359/23f4e/Functions.jpg 1860w,\n/static/f8e5e063265e9bce9de8ad1b54603359/6b48d/Functions.jpg 1940w"}}}}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2744294623","3114762285","550521386","764694655"]}